node.text: @weiweiinsg 谢谢妳！真的为她高兴，接近梦想更近一步了！

Budae Jjigae prepared by girl in celebration of her being offered medicine course in University. It has been her dream to be a doctor since young to help humanity and save lives.
.

Though also being offered Dentistry course which is even more difficult to get in than medicine, she gave up this easier path and shorter course. This covid19 has not frightened her or waver her decision to become a doctor. We are really proud of her courage and determination! Thank God for his blessings and leading her to do a course where her heart desires! .

Swipe to the last pic to see the surprise delivery that the school sprang on her yesterday. What a sweet gesture that brightens up one’s day! 😍
@ariane.le Thanks Ariane! Yes she worked really hard all by herself and never has any tuition. I saw her efforts and rewarded her a Korea trip in Jan even before A levels result was out in Feb! 😄
Wow congrats to your girl!!! 🥳🎉🎊 She must have worked very hard for this! Glad that all her hard work and effort paid off!
@missionbake Thanks Jeannie! Really happy for her as she is a step closer to her dreams. 😊
Wow! Congrats! Such an awesome news to share👍🏻👏🏻
@dressacake she offered to treat us and bought everything herself and prepared it too. Also if she prepares, she can buy the things she will eat only! (*notice no spring onion??😂)
Our fave! I thought you should be cooking to celebrate! 😂
@poohbear1005 Thank you! Praise God for leading her to her heart’s desire and working towards her dream. 😊
@florencesjah Thanks Florence! She is a step closer to her dreams! 😊
Omg congrats to your girl 😍 Medicine somemore!
@funwithflavourz Thank you & a good Sunday to you! 😊
That is awesome!!! So happy for your daughter! Congratulations! 😍
@weiweiinsg 谢谢妳！真的为她高兴，接近梦想更近一步了！
